Generate count distinct blog post ideas for the brief below. Each idea needs a title (≤80 chars), a 1-2 sentence summary, and 3-7 outline points covering the post arc. Respect tone if provided. Avoid topics in existingIdeasContext.
Inputs:
- brief: {{ brief }}
- audience: {{ audience }}
- count: {{ count }}
- tone: {{ tone }}
- existingIdeasContext: {{ existingIdeasContext }}
- referenceContent: {{ referenceContent }}
- contextSlotBindings: {{ contextSlotBindings }}

Write a blog draft from the following inputs.
Inputs:
- idea: {{ idea }}
- tone: {{ tone }}
- length: {{ length }}
- referenceContent: {{ referenceContent }}
- audience: {{ audience }}
- voice: {{ voice }}
- sources: {{ sources }}
- contextSlotBindings: {{ contextSlotBindings }}

Generate {{ count }} blog-image prompts for the supplied draft.

Draft (JSON): {{ draft }}

Distribute the prompts across these placements (default: cover, inline, social): {{ placements }}

Visual style guidance (may be empty): {{ style }}

Brand keywords to weave in (may be empty array): {{ brandKeywords }}

Return ONLY the JSON object specified in SKILL.md — keys: prompts (array of {placement, prompt, rationale}), notes (string).
- contextSlotBindings: {{ contextSlotBindings }}

Write a promotional LinkedIn post from the following inputs.
Inputs:
- postTitle: {{ postTitle }}
- blogPostUrl: {{ blogPostUrl }}
- companyUrl: {{ companyUrl }}
- postExcerpt: {{ postExcerpt }}
- blogPostContent: {{ blogPostContent }}
- destinationType: {{ destinationType }}
- destinationName: {{ destinationName }}
